dBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:23:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>各位巴打絲打比d意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想再繼續練習下，睇睇可唔可以幫補家計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/22/011939_7d4ab5137f2b9a1fd090ff41b13c3e28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F22%2F011939_7d4ab5137f2b9a1fd090ff41b13c3e28.jpg&h=9051ce06&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n又想用腦魔賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁又唔係淨係勾左腦魔既，只不過覺得依隻幾好睇。<br />\n如果大家有興趣俾多啲大家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c328e11e5cc1cac31b8ebcd2473f50c307a2016d","tid":443632,"uid":26436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:28:04.000Z","msg":"幾得意但係本身唔識腦魔既人第一眼可能淨係會望到兩隻巨大眼白，可能會嚇親，建議眼珠可以大少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc53696abdba7acd58ff43c7d2143ca8d644047","tid":443632,"uid":42817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:30:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾得意但係本身唔識腦魔既人第一眼可能淨係會望到兩隻巨大眼白，可能會嚇親，建議眼珠可以大少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日開始勾第二隻，等我試試佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413e5cc4d1d6017da51481c06d1e99014f47b44c","tid":443632,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T17:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2746553a3b70960d438958e5bb3691408f7033f","tid":443632,"uid":51371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T1